## Specialized Options

**Jirafeau** - Ultra-simple one-click sharing

- Upload → Get link → Share
- No accounts needed
- Optional password + expiry
- Minimal resource usage

**Sharry** - For recurring shares with groups

- Share files with multiple people
- Track who downloaded what
- Email notifications
- Good for team/client file drops

**Chibisafe** - If you want something beautiful

- Gorgeous modern UI
- Albums and organization
- User accounts (optional)
- Great for image/media sharing
